 Version 1.0 (29 November 2010)
* Initial release.
  . User manual.
  . Library (librec).
  . Utilities: recinf, recsel, recins, recdel, recset, recfix, csv2rec,
    mdb2rec.
  . Experimental Emacs mode (rec-mode.el).
